1. *Prvog* dana novembra nastavila je škola. (On the first day of November, school continued.)

2. Biće mnogo više radosti *prvog* dana leta. (There will be a lot more joy on the first day of summer.)

3. *Prvog* dana decembra svi su se veselili. (On the first day of December, everyone was happy.)

4. *Prvog* puta smo se upoznali pre tri godine. (We met for the first time three years ago.)

5. Nismo se sreli *prvog* dana. (We didn't meet on the first day.)

6. *Prvog* dana je bilo puno snega. (On the first day, there was a lot of snow.)